OL,5,G1650 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FAt Cross Farm Cottages in
OL,7,     FHolmfirth, Claire reckons she can
OL,8,     Fpip her rivals to the post. But
OL,9,     FPete and Alex get antsy about the
OL,10,     FArtex, while Malaya has a firm
OL,11,     Fopinion about his mattress.
OL,12,G1720 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FAt the New Valron Hotel in
OL,14,     FBlackpool, Malaya hopes that the
OL,15,     Fseaside setting will blow his
OL,16,     Frivals out of the water. But a
OL,17,     Fproblem with the pipes sends the
OL,18,     Fscores down the tubes...
