OL,5,G1750 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FPhil and Maria hope that their
OL,7,     Fswish sense of style will impress
OL,8,     Ftheir guests at The Spinney
OL,9,     FHomestay in Warwickshire. On a
OL,10,     Fpedalo trip, the rivalry revs up
OL,11,     Fwith some raucous racing.
OL,12,G1820 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FThe B&Bers meet to settle some
OL,14,     Fscores and find out who's won.
OL,15,     FDirty discoveries and sleep issues
OL,16,     Fare on the agenda, and one payment
OL,17,     Fin particular leaves Phil and
OL,18,     FMaria out in the cold.
